        "subject": "LU-7988 hsm: defer all new hals",
        "message": "LU-7988 hsm: defer all new hals\n\nThe HALs are enqueued on a coordinator list, and the coordinator will\nprocess them once every \"wait_event_time\" seconds. This reduces the\nnumber of times hsm_find_compatible and thus cdt_llog_process are\ncalled.\n\nTest-Parameters: testlist=sanity-hsm\nSigned-off-by: frank zago <fzago@cray.com>\nChange-Id: I0edbf0d2847d320fee20e22c637a49ea27397ab1\n"
